data.description: You will love Grand Lake! Gorgeous views,quiet & peaceful! 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, full brick home backs up to wooded preserve. Gourmet Kitchen w/ lots of cabinets & granite countertops, double ovens & stainless steel appliances. Primary bedroom on main level with spacious bath. Office, dining, family room, kitchen & laundry on main level. Upstairs is an oversized bonus room, 3 additional bedrooms, jack n jill bath and tons of storage. Out back you can enjoy screen in porch and patio area plus a detached shed.
